llama3.1.reason: The film Zookeeper (2011) primarily revolves around a romantic comedy storyline with talking animals, rather than being set in a zoo. While the movie does feature a zookeeper as its main character and takes place at a zoo, it's not focused on films set in zoos but rather on a different aspect of filmmaking.
